            <div class="help-section">
                <h2>Trending questions</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">How do I get my mobile transfer tickets I bought on StubHub?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">I sold tickets on StubHub. When do I have to deliver them to the buyer?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">I sold a type of mobile ticket on StubHub. How do I deliver it to the buyer?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">How can I send tickets I bought on StubHub to a friend?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">I bought tickets on StubHub as a guest. How do I see my order?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">What happens if events are postponed or rescheduled?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">I sold mobile transfer or Flash Seats (AXS) tickets on StubHub and transferred them to the buyer. They haven't accepted the tickets yet.</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

